		<description><![CDATA[It has taken me a few weeks to catch up with Todd&#039;s webcast.
I have really enjoyed the lessons Todd has done with SBL, so was looking forward to this interview.
Todd comes accross in the interview as he has with the classes: a genuinely nice and humble man who has put himself through a lot to learn what he knows, and is keen and willing to share his knowledge with anyone else who is hungry to learn.
Thanks to Todd for being Todd, and to Scott for being so broad-minded as to bring in other bass educators to help us students on our journey with bass.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It has taken me a few weeks to catch up with Todd&#8217;s webcast.<br />
I have really enjoyed the lessons Todd has done with SBL, so was looking forward to this interview.<br />
Todd comes accross in the interview as he has with the classes: a genuinely nice and humble man who has put himself through a lot to learn what he knows, and is keen and willing to share his knowledge with anyone else who is hungry to learn.<br />
Thanks to Todd for being Todd, and to Scott for being so broad-minded as to bring in other bass educators to help us students on our journey with bass.</p>
